dct_title_s: Pacific Coast, Santa Rosa Island to Point Buchon, California
dct_alternative_sm: Santa Rosa Island to Point Buchon
dct_description_sm: F.M. Thorn, superintendent ; verified B.A. Colonna, assistant in charge of Office.
Relief shown by hachures and shading; depths shown by soundings.
Covers San Miguel Island, east part of Santa Rosa Island, and coastline north from Point Conception.
Oriented with north toward upper right.
Includes charts and notes on lighthouses, buoys, tides, etc.
